These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
There 4 different types of food: zucchini, potato, cauliflower, corn
There are 4 different nationalities: french, japanese, colombian, pakistani
1. the japanese is on the left of the french##1
2. the person eating zucchini is the pakistani##1
3. the colombian is on the right of the french##1
4. the person eating potato is on the left of the pakistani##1
5. the person eating corn is on the left of the french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | corn | cauliflower | potato | zucchini   |
| Nationality   | japanese  | french     | colombian   | pakistani |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, puzzles, sudoku, baking
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, baseball, weightlifting, ice-hockey
1. the person who's hobby is baking is the person who's sport is baseball##1
2. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
4. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
5. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | sudoku | baking | puzzles | dancing    |
| Sport   | weightlifting    | baseball      | handball | ice-hockey |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, board-games, cooking, dancing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, martial-arts, scientific, zombie
1. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person watching superhero movies##1
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the far right##1
4. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Hobby         | filmmaking | dancing | cooking   | board-games |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero   | scientific | zombie | martial-arts         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, thriller, martial-arts, romance
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, swimming, climbing, ice-hockey
1. the person who's sport is swimming is the person watching romance movies##1
2. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
3. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
4. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
5. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | romance | thriller | spy  | martial-arts      |
| Sport         | swimming | ice-hockey   | climbing | cricket |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-5::.
There 4 different types of food: plum, onion, radish, cabbage
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, snake, rat, chinchilla
1. the person eating onion is on the left of the person eating plum##1
2. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person eating radish##1
3. the person eating cabbage is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
4. the owner of the snake is on the right of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |    3     |      4      |
| Food   | cabbage | radish | onion | plum |
| Pet    | rabbit       | chinchilla | rat | snake     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, colombian, french, american
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, rabbit, horse, turtle
1. the colombian is on the far right##1
2. the american is on the left of the french##1
3. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
4. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the french##1
5. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the owner of the horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Nationality   | american | french | malaysian | colombian |
| Pet           | chinchilla      | horse | turtle | rabbit    |

