.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, house, pop, hip-hop
4 different pets are kept: pony, dog, goldfish, horse
1. the owner of the goldfish is on the far left##1
2. the fan of hip-hop is on the far right##1
3. the fan of pop is on the far left##1
4. the owner of the dog is on the far right##1
5. the fan of house is on the left of the owner of the horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |     3     |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | pop | house | techno | hip-hop  |
| Pet           | goldfish | pony | horse       | dog |

