.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  project-manager, nurse, software-developer, fisherman
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, skateboard, bus, bike
1. the person driving the bike is on the right of the nurse##1
2. the person driving the bike is the fisherman##1
3. the nurse is on the right of the project-manager##1
4. the software-developer is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
5. the person driving the ship is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |    3     |    4     |
| Job         | software-developer | project-manager      | nurse | fisherman |
| Transport   | ship          | skateboard | bus     | bike    |

