.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-9::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, comedy, epic, documentary
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, quad-bike, trike, skateboard
1. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the van##1
2. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person driving the van##1
3. the person watching documentary movies is on the far right##1
4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
5. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |   3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy    | epic       | action | documentary   |
| Transport     | quad-bike | trike | skateboard   | van |

