.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, lemonade, 7up, iced-tea
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, helicopter, quad-bike, scooter
1. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
3. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |       3       |   4    |
| Beverage    | juice | 7up  | lemonade | iced-tea |
| Transport   | scooter | quad-bike | helicopter          | subway    |

