.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, almond-milk, soy-milk, lemonade
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, rock, soul, metal
1. the fan of soul is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
2. the fan of metal is on the right of the fan of soul##1
3. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is the fan of soul##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |       3       |   4   |
| Beverage      | soy-milk | almond-milk  | mirinda | lemonade |
| Music-Genre   | salsa  | soul | metal           | rock   |

