2. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
3. the person watching fantasy movies is the person who's hobby is baking##1
4. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
5. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | skydiving | baking | fishing | photography |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure     | fantasy    | mystery      | superhero   |

