.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
There are 4 different nationalities: german, colombian, malaysian, canadian
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, bus, taxi, skateboard
1. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the colombian##1
2. the person driving the bus is on the left of the canadian##1
3. the german is on the left of the malaysian##1
4. the canadian is the person driving the skateboard##1
5. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the colombian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Nationality   | german | malaysian | colombian | canadian   |
| Transport     | taxi  | jet-ski    | bus       | skateboard |

 